<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="29400000t" end="35800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">柯妮</p>
<p begin="425800000t" end="449000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">(還能爭取多少自由)</p>
<p begin="532600000t" end="571400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">「約定的夢幻島」</p>
<p begin="604600000t" end="613400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">(Fire)</p>
<p begin="619800000t" end="642200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(該我出場了　率先上陣)</p>
<p begin="643000000t" end="666600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(在知道何謂失敗之前)</p>
<p begin="667400000t" end="695400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(先找到導火線)</p>
<p begin="696200000t" end="707800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="708600000t" end="737800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(沒有神明可崇拜　也沒有星星)</p>
<p begin="738600000t" end="763800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(但是從沒放棄祈求)</p>
<p begin="764600000t" end="791400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(因害怕後悔而停滯的腳步)</p>
<p begin="792200000t" end="802200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="803000000t" end="850600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(想忘記的正是無法忘掉的事)</p>
<p begin="851400000t" end="897400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(通往天堂之路始於地獄)</p>
<p begin="898200000t" end="945000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(一點火花化為熊熊烈火)</p>
<p begin="945800000t" end="978600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(緊張不安地不斷追趕)</p>
<p begin="979400000t" end="1003000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">(奔往未來)</p>
<p begin="1003800000t" end="1025400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">(儘管只是數厘米)</p>
<p begin="1026200000t" end="1049000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">(也要朝著願望中的目的地)</p>
<p begin="1049800000t" end="1072600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="1100600000t" end="1147000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">(為內心贖罪　勸自己放棄)</p>
<p begin="1147800000t" end="1168200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">(這樣將來還能說甚麼)</p>
<p begin="1194600000t" end="1216200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="1305000000t" end="1336600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">早安…　　快些</p>
<p begin="1337400000t" end="1352600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">菲爾，不要在這裡跑</p>
<p begin="1353400000t" end="1376600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">這隻放這邊嗎　　是，麻煩你了</p>
<p begin="1389800000t" end="1407400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">馬克，你幫忙放好碟子</p>
<p begin="1408200000t" end="1418200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">知道了，媽媽</p>
<p begin="1491400000t" end="1503000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">早安，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="1557400000t" end="1569400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">笑一下吧，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="1606600000t" end="1617800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">記住，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="1623000000t" end="1639400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">要表現得好像平時那樣</p>
<p begin="1645800000t" end="1668200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">記住我們昨天是違反規則</p>
<p begin="1669000000t" end="1678200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">去了門那邊</p>
<p begin="1687800000t" end="1699800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">但是甚麼也看不到</p>
<p begin="1710600000t" end="1733000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">不過那隻小兔兔玩偶…</p>
<p begin="1733800000t" end="1764600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">這個…媽媽肯定已經發現了它</p>
<p begin="1765400000t" end="1783800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">不過她應該還未知道</p>
<p begin="1784600000t" end="1794600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">這件事是誰做的</p>
<p begin="1800200000t" end="1819000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">媽媽還在笑</p>
<p begin="1819800000t" end="1842600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">她的表情完全看不出有甚麼</p>
<p begin="1843400000t" end="1859000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">所以我們也要這樣做</p>
<p begin="1868200000t" end="1887000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">表情有問題，媽媽就會發現</p>
<p begin="1903800000t" end="1923400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">絕對不可以輸，笑吧</p>
<p begin="1985800000t" end="1995000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">美味的飼料</p>
<p begin="2003400000t" end="2021000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">穿著很易髒的白色衣服</p>
<p begin="2026200000t" end="2043400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">每天過著有規律的生活</p>
<p begin="2054200000t" end="2071000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">全部都是為了要保持我們</p>
<p begin="2071800000t" end="2087800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">身為商品應有的品質</p>
<p begin="2096200000t" end="2109800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">我們的命運就是</p>
<p begin="2110600000t" end="2135000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">默默等待，一個一個被他們送出欄</p>
<p begin="2140200000t" end="2170600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">不是這樣的，那隻鬼當時說過</p>
<p begin="2171400000t" end="2181800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">「又是六歲」</p>
<p begin="2182600000t" end="2205400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">「出欄的都是品質一般的普通貨」</p>
<p begin="2206200000t" end="2213400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">那麼即是…</p>
<p begin="2214200000t" end="2235000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">單從這句話來看</p>
<p begin="2235800000t" end="2255800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">我們的年齡應該就是我們的等級</p>
<p begin="2264200000t" end="2283400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">如果我的記憶沒錯</p>
<p begin="2284200000t" end="2301000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">所有被送出欄的年齡</p>
<p begin="2301800000t" end="2314600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">都是6至12歲之間</p>
<p begin="2321800000t" end="2345400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">所以如果六歲等於普通貨</p>
<p begin="2346200000t" end="2379000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">那麼最頂級的就即是…　　12歲</p>
<p begin="2379800000t" end="2393800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">那麼分數又代表甚麼</p>
<p begin="2394600000t" end="2409800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">就算在測驗裡拿到高分</p>
<p begin="2410600000t" end="2430200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">肉質也不會比較美味</p>
<p begin="2431000000t" end="2450600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">沒錯，只公布滿分</p>
<p begin="2451400000t" end="2464600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">沒有公布其他分數</p>
<p begin="2465400000t" end="2477800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">應該就是這樣</p>
<p begin="2488200000t" end="2498200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">出欄順序？</p>
<p begin="2508200000t" end="2519400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">超過六歲的</p>
<p begin="2520200000t" end="2544200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">就會由分數最低的開始順序出貨</p>
<p begin="2551000000t" end="2575400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">然後到了12歲的小朋友</p>
<p begin="2576200000t" end="2592200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">就會無條件被送出欄</p>
<p begin="2593000000t" end="2614200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">即是說因為我們拿到滿分</p>
<p begin="2615000000t" end="2627800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">才沒有被人送出欄嗎</p>
<p begin="2640200000t" end="2651000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">但是我不明白</p>
<p begin="2657400000t" end="2676200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">為甚麼要按分數順序</p>
<p begin="2696600000t" end="2712200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">6歲至12歲這一點</p>
<p begin="2713000000t" end="2727800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">有甚麼特別意義嗎</p>
<p begin="2735800000t" end="2753400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">難道是體形的大小</p>
<p begin="2759400000t" end="2781400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">不，那會否跟體重有關</p>
<p begin="2813800000t" end="2825000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">是人腦的大小</p>
<p begin="2842600000t" end="2850200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">那即是…</p>
<p begin="2851000000t" end="2869800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">可能因為人腦是最美味的</p>
<p begin="2876600000t" end="2901800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">而且越發達的人腦就…</p>
<p begin="2912600000t" end="2937400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">他們會吃人腦？</p>
<p begin="2938200000t" end="2957000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">所以無論有甚麼風險</p>
<p begin="2957800000t" end="2974200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">和多少成本也沒關係</p>
<p begin="2975000000t" end="2990600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">因為我們都是屬於高級品</p>
<p begin="2996200000t" end="3013000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">你認真想想，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="3013800000t" end="3035000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">回想剛剛出了欄的柯妮</p>
<p begin="3035800000t" end="3051400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">還有之前的阿豪</p>
<p begin="3052200000t" end="3068600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">跟再之前的賽蒂</p>
<p begin="3069400000t" end="3088600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">直到今天為止的週期</p>
<p begin="3089400000t" end="3104600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">預計下次出欄的日子</p>
<p begin="3105400000t" end="3118600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">最快會在兩個月後</p>
<p begin="3119400000t" end="3144200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">即是我們要在期限之前</p>
<p begin="3145000000t" end="3168600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">想到可以帶全部小朋友逃走的方法</p>
<p begin="3244200000t" end="3269400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">我們將這塊土地簡單地畫出來</p>
<p begin="3271400000t" end="3293400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">孤兒院在中間，門在這邊</p>
<p begin="3294200000t" end="3312600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">這裡四周都被森林包圍</p>
<p begin="3321800000t" end="3341000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">首先要考慮從哪裡逃走</p>
<p begin="3347000000t" end="3362600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">選門，還是森林</p>
<p begin="3375400000t" end="3407000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">我們就選森林，除了出欄之外</p>
<p begin="3407800000t" end="3423000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">其他時間門都不會打開</p>
<p begin="3423800000t" end="3447400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">而門打開時…　　怪物會在那裡</p>
<p begin="3453000000t" end="3469800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">那麼該在何時從森林逃走</p>
<p begin="3476600000t" end="3486600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">逃走的時間</p>
<p begin="3487400000t" end="3497000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">是我們可以自由活動的</p>
<p begin="3497800000t" end="3509800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">日間遊玩時間</p>
<p begin="3516600000t" end="3530200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">還是媽媽不在這裡的出欄之夜</p>
<p begin="3531000000t" end="3547800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">不可以在出欄之夜逃走</p>
<p begin="3548600000t" end="3566600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">那麼會有一個人成為犧牲品</p>
<p begin="3571800000t" end="3602600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">也是，我也擔心年幼的小朋友</p>
<p begin="3603400000t" end="3617400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">晚上會捱不了睏</p>
<p begin="3629000000t" end="3638200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">就這樣說定了</p>
<p begin="3641800000t" end="3661000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">日間穿過森林出去外面</p>
<p begin="3661800000t" end="3678200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">至於計劃能否實現</p>
<p begin="3679000000t" end="3701400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">那就要視乎接下來的實際情況</p>
<p begin="3848600000t" end="3857000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">諾曼</p>
<p begin="3913400000t" end="3933000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">諾曼，沒事吧</p>
<p begin="3948600000t" end="3973800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">可能是要考慮的事太多，有點累</p>
<p begin="4003800000t" end="4022600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">真是的，那沒辦法了</p>
<p begin="4068200000t" end="4087400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">怎樣？上面有甚麼</p>
<p begin="4095000000t" end="4106200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">甚麼也沒有</p>
<p begin="4111000000t" end="4122600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">不過這道牆</p>
<p begin="4123400000t" end="4143000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">闊度大約有兩至三米</p>
<p begin="4143800000t" end="4161800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">而且還非常高</p>
<p begin="4162600000t" end="4182200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">但是沒有任何人看守</p>
<p begin="4197000000t" end="4205000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">很安靜</p>
<p begin="4223800000t" end="4239800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">艾瑪，你有甚麼想法</p>
<p begin="4264200000t" end="4278200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">牆身堅硬穩固</p>
<p begin="4284200000t" end="4309400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">沒有任何凹凸不平的位置或罅隙</p>
<p begin="4310200000t" end="4327400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">再加上牆身表面很光滑</p>
<p begin="4333400000t" end="4353400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">一般來說肯定爬不上去</p>
<p begin="4354200000t" end="4372200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">那麼要放棄嗎</p>
<p begin="4373000000t" end="4397800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">雖然建造這道牆就是想我們放棄</p>
<p begin="4398600000t" end="4413800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">但是我想我跟諾曼</p>
<p begin="4414600000t" end="4441000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">只要有一根繩就有辦法爬上去</p>
<p begin="4441800000t" end="4461000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">附近好像都沒有鬼在</p>
<p begin="4461800000t" end="4477400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">只有媽媽一個看守</p>
<p begin="4483000000t" end="4496200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">不會有問題，不用怕</p>
<p begin="4594200000t" end="4609400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">為甚麼還欠兩個人</p>
<p begin="4610200000t" end="4625000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">媽媽</p>
<p begin="4637400000t" end="4670600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">馬克，發生了甚麼事</p>
<p begin="4679000000t" end="4689000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="4689800000t" end="4717000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">我在森林裡跟奈拉走散了</p>
<p begin="4717800000t" end="4748200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">我找了她很久，但還是找不到她</p>
<p begin="4812600000t" end="4824200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">她不會有事的</p>
<p begin="4847400000t" end="4865800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">大家繼續留在這裡，不要走開</p>
<p begin="4873000000t" end="4881000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">聽到嗎</p>
<p begin="4923800000t" end="4931800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">媽媽</p>
<p begin="5037400000t" end="5058200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">媽媽　　奈拉</p>
<p begin="5059000000t" end="5079000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">其實她只是累得睡著了</p>
<p begin="5079800000t" end="5118600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">你看，她完全沒受傷　　太好了</p>
<p begin="5125000000t" end="5151790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">對不起…奈拉</p>
<p begin="5157800000t" end="5175000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">媽媽剛才的表現</p>
<p begin="5175800000t" end="5207800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">簡直就好像知道奈拉所在的位置</p>
<p begin="5208600000t" end="5235000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">說得沒錯，說起來從一開始</p>
<p begin="5235800000t" end="5243000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">媽媽玩捉迷藏</p>
<p begin="5243800000t" end="5260600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">就很擅長找到我們的位置</p>
<p begin="5269800000t" end="5282200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">不管躲在哪裡</p>
<p begin="5283000000t" end="5297800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">都會很快被她找到</p>
<p begin="5298600000t" end="5335400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">那個不是陀錶，而是發訊器</p>
<p begin="5345000000t" end="5362200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">我們身體裡某個地方</p>
<p begin="5363000000t" end="5382600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">可能已經植入了發訊器</p>
<p begin="5383400000t" end="5412600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">而媽媽就是為了讓我們知道這件事</p>
<p begin="5413400000t" end="5437000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">才會刻意展示那小盒子給我們看</p>
<p begin="5445800000t" end="5460200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">「無論是誰也逃不掉」</p>
<p begin="5468600000t" end="5493400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">媽媽想傳遞的就是這個訊息</p>
<p begin="5553000000t" end="5580200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">媽媽是…　　敵人</p>
<p begin="5678200000t" end="5697800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">首先我們要準備一根繩</p>
<p begin="5698600000t" end="5715000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我大概知道哪裡會有繩</p>
<p begin="5720600000t" end="5743000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">今晚10時，在走廊…　　等等</p>
<p begin="5755400000t" end="5777400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">既然我們有可能被人植入發訊器</p>
<p begin="5778200000t" end="5792600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">那即是這裡也會有攝影機</p>
<p begin="5793400000t" end="5808600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">或者偷聽器的東西</p>
<p begin="5809400000t" end="5841400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">不用擔心，我徹底找過孤兒院這裡</p>
<p begin="5842200000t" end="5858200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">但是沒發現類似的裝置</p>
<p begin="5859000000t" end="5870200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">你何時找的</p>
<p begin="5871000000t" end="5889800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">但是我實在太大意</p>
<p begin="5890600000t" end="5910600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">我沒想過被人做手腳的</p>
<p begin="5911400000t" end="5927800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">並不是這幢建築物，而是我們</p>
<p begin="5945400000t" end="5962200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">已經暴露了嗎</p>
<p begin="5963000000t" end="5983400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">剛才我們去過牆那邊的事</p>
<p begin="5993800000t" end="6023800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">沒事的，因為那時候也沒有暴露</p>
<p begin="6034200000t" end="6059000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">我是指送小兔兔去給柯妮那次</p>
<p begin="6066600000t" end="6073400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">說得對</p>
<p begin="6079800000t" end="6097000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">媽媽也不是經常可以掌握</p>
<p begin="6097800000t" end="6113000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">我們的位置</p>
<p begin="6119000000t" end="6129000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">她需要確認了</p>
<p begin="6129800000t" end="6144600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">才會知道我們的位置</p>
<p begin="6151000000t" end="6169800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">雖然現在已經被媽媽發現了</p>
<p begin="6170600000t" end="6197000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">我們當中有人曾將小兔兔拿去那裡</p>
<p begin="6208600000t" end="6244600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">但是我想她還未確定這人是誰</p>
<p begin="6245400000t" end="6273800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">不然也不會用這麼婉轉的警告方式</p>
<p begin="6274600000t" end="6283000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">原來如此</p>
<p begin="6290600000t" end="6315800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">諾曼，有空嗎</p>
<p begin="6316600000t" end="6339000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">時鐘好像有點壞掉了</p>
<p begin="6339800000t" end="6359800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">知道了，我一會去看看</p>
<p begin="6367000000t" end="6378600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">不會有事的，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="6385800000t" end="6402600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">我們沒受到懷疑</p>
<p begin="6526600000t" end="6535400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">柯妮</p>
<p begin="6603000000t" end="6607800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">艾…</p>
<p begin="6665800000t" end="6678600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">你怎麼了？艾瑪</p>
<p begin="6679400000t" end="6697400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">你的臉色不太好</p>
<p begin="6727400000t" end="6752600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">說起來，你今早跟平時不同</p>
<p begin="6753400000t" end="6772200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">看起來好像沒精打采</p>
<p begin="6774600000t" end="6783800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">我沒事</p>
<p begin="6922600000t" end="6935400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">我真的沒事</p>
<p begin="6941800000t" end="6968200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">只是我想到很快就會離開孤兒院</p>
<p begin="6969000000t" end="6984600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">覺得有點寂寞而已</p>
<p begin="7008200000t" end="7027000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">艾瑪，你喜歡孤兒院嗎</p>
<p begin="7027800000t" end="7048600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">我最喜歡孤兒院和媽媽</p>
<p begin="7076600000t" end="7103000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">柯妮…不知道她現在怎樣</p>
<p begin="7175000000t" end="7200200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">柯妮說她日後長大之後</p>
<p begin="7201000000t" end="7225400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">想當一個像媽媽這樣的母親</p>
<p begin="7270200000t" end="7288200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">對，我也知道</p>
<p begin="7295800000t" end="7325000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">柯妮一定會成為一個優雅的女性</p>
<p begin="7325800000t" end="7341000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">她會是個溫柔的媽媽</p>
<p begin="7375800000t" end="7399000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">媽媽，晚餐已經準備好了</p>
<p begin="7430600000t" end="7442600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">等我</p>
<p begin="7443400000t" end="7465400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">我一會兒就去　　快些</p>
<p begin="7499000000t" end="7511400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">艾瑪，走吧</p>
<p begin="7557000000t" end="7593800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">你們昨天去過門那邊嗎</p>
<p begin="7616200000t" end="7644200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">我們不會去，那是規則</p>
<p begin="7650200000t" end="7675800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">我們昨天跟大家玩捉迷藏玩得忘形</p>
<p begin="7676600000t" end="7692600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">對嗎　　說得對</p>
<p begin="7693400000t" end="7702600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">為甚麼這樣問</p>
<p begin="7723400000t" end="7743800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">沒甚麼，你們沒去就好</p>
<p begin="7921000000t" end="7929400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">先起來吧</p>
<p begin="8534200000t" end="8555000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">你真的很聰明，諾曼</p>
<p begin="8557400000t" end="8572200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">竟然想到用桌布</p>
<p begin="8577400000t" end="8595000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">這可以用來代替繩</p>
<p begin="8661000000t" end="8679800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">這樣我們就可以越過這道牆</p>
<p begin="8700200000t" end="8727400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">好，接下來的才是難題</p>
<p begin="8728200000t" end="8745800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">找出發訊器的位置，還有…</p>
<p begin="8746600000t" end="8769400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">帶著全部人一起逃走的方法</p>
<p begin="8775400000t" end="8782600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">諾曼</p>
<p begin="8795000000t" end="8823000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">其實我們也可以對阿雷說這件事嗎</p>
<p begin="8829000000t" end="8841400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">我也有考慮過這點</p>
<p begin="8850200000t" end="8863800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">阿雷應該不會覺得驚訝</p>
<p begin="8864600000t" end="8873400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">和不知怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="8879000000t" end="8900200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">他知識廣博，而且精通機械</p>
<p begin="8908600000t" end="8921400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">他一定能幫我們</p>
<p begin="8933800000t" end="8953000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">不過…　　不過？</p>
<p begin="8957400000t" end="8978600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">這件事就讓我來跟阿雷說</p>
<p begin="8979400000t" end="8993000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">艾瑪，你現在先回去孤兒院</p>
<p begin="8993800000t" end="9001000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">為甚麼</p>
<p begin="9016200000t" end="9022600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">阿雷</p>
<p begin="9047400000t" end="9053000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">你們好</p>
<p begin="9091600000t" end="9109200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">對不起，跟著你們來</p>
<p begin="9126000000t" end="9139200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">我留意了很久</p>
<p begin="9146000000t" end="9161200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">打算詳細問清楚</p>
<p begin="9231200000t" end="9252800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">那晚在門那邊發生了甚麼事</p>
<p begin="9260400000t" end="9266400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">我的意思是</p>
<p begin="9267200000t" end="9286800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">你們去送小免免給柯妮那晚</p>
<p begin="9292000000t" end="9319200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">因為你們明顯地表現得古古怪怪</p>
<p begin="9320000000t" end="9331600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">明明說趕不及</p>
<p begin="9332400000t" end="9347200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">但是又兩手空空地回來</p>
<p begin="9352400000t" end="9363600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">觀察力很強</p>
<p begin="9364400000t" end="9392400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">沒可能會沒事發生過的，快些說</p>
<p begin="9393200000t" end="9413200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">阿雷果然是很聰明的人</p>
<p begin="9498800000t" end="9520400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">鬼，農場…</p>
<p begin="9531600000t" end="9545200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">媽媽是敵人？</p>
<p begin="9564400000t" end="9573200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">那不是很糟糕嗎</p>
<p begin="9574000000t" end="9586000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">這麼快就能接受？</p>
<p begin="9588400000t" end="9606000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">意思即是我們都是</p>
<p begin="9606800000t" end="9627200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">從小就一直受到悉心照料和管理</p>
<p begin="9632400000t" end="9657200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">最後提供給鬼吃的糧食嗎</p>
<p begin="9658000000t" end="9675200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">但是你怎會這麼輕易</p>
<p begin="9676000000t" end="9693200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">就完全相信我們的說話</p>
<p begin="9702800000t" end="9712400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">當然相信</p>
<p begin="9718400000t" end="9741600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">諾曼又怎麼會說這樣荒謬的謊話</p>
<p begin="9748800000t" end="9760400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">艾瑪說的就未必</p>
<p begin="9786800000t" end="9812800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">不過實際上要逃走時</p>
<p begin="9813600000t" end="9832800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">就會出現各種各樣的問題</p>
<p begin="9833600000t" end="9846400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">第一個問題是人數</p>
<p begin="9854000000t" end="9872400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">只可以帶走能實現計劃的人</p>
<p begin="9873200000t" end="9882000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">等等</p>
<p begin="9905600000t" end="9923600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">我想帶全部人一起走</p>
<p begin="9930000000t" end="9946400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">你幫幫我們吧，阿雷</p>
<p begin="9970400000t" end="9992000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">全部人？你說笑吧</p>
<p begin="10006000000t" end="10022400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">總共有37個小朋友</p>
<p begin="10029600000t" end="10049200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">當中還要大部分未夠六歲</p>
<p begin="10052400000t" end="10078400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">媽媽、鬼、發訊器</p>
<p begin="10085600000t" end="10108800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">這個逃走計劃本來就不容易成功</p>
<p begin="10109600000t" end="10121600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">這樣會變得難上加難</p>
<p begin="10122400000t" end="10137600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">這點我也知道</p>
<p begin="10138400000t" end="10152400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">但不是沒可能做得到</p>
<p begin="10153200000t" end="10165200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">就是沒可能</p>
<p begin="10166000000t" end="10191200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">艾瑪，你應該沒察覺吧</p>
<p begin="10201600000t" end="10210400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">阿雷，等等</p>
<p begin="10222000000t" end="10234000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">原來如此</p>
<p begin="10234800000t" end="10251190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">所以你說「讓我來跟阿雷說」</p>
<p begin="10267600000t" end="10286800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">這種事還是說清楚會比較好</p>
<p begin="10292400000t" end="10308800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">艾瑪　　甚麼事</p>
<p begin="10314000000t" end="10337600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">其實我們光是離開這裡是不夠的</p>
<p begin="10338390000t" end="10352400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">這即是甚麼意思</p>
<p begin="10358800000t" end="10387200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">我們不知道外面實際的情況是怎樣</p>
<p begin="10393190000t" end="10410790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">我們出欄是有目的地</p>
<p begin="10416800000t" end="10437600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">現在憑著有農場存在這點</p>
<p begin="10438390000t" end="10449200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">應該就可以想得到</p>
<p begin="10459600000t" end="10478800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">外面等著我們的是鬼的社會</p>
<p begin="10485200000t" end="10496000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">最壞的情況可能是</p>
<p begin="10496800000t" end="10519200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">根本就沒有人類能夠生存的空間</p>
<p begin="10544000000t" end="10554400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">沒可能做得到</p>
<p begin="10560800000t" end="10570800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">已經可以預知</p>
<p begin="10571600000t" end="10587600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">帶他們出去會全軍覆沒</p>
<p begin="10599200000t" end="10620000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">留他們在這裡是最好的辦法</p>
<p begin="10641600000t" end="10648800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">不行</p>
<p begin="10665600000t" end="10674400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">就算沒可能</p>
<p begin="10675200000t" end="10692400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">我也想帶全部人離開</p>
<p begin="10693200000t" end="10706800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">我們再想辦法</p>
<p begin="10717600000t" end="10734800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">我不要全軍覆沒</p>
<p begin="10735600000t" end="10756800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">留他們在這裡也不是選擇之一</p>
<p begin="10772400000t" end="10793200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">我希望柯妮是最後一個犧牲者</p>
<p begin="10800000000t" end="10815200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">我不想再看到</p>
<p begin="10816000000t" end="10832400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">有其他人變成她這樣</p>
<p begin="10840400000t" end="10863200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">外面沒有的，就自己創造出來</p>
<p begin="10864000000t" end="10880000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">創造人類能生存的地方</p>
<p begin="10887600000t" end="10909600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">由我們來改變世界　　你…</p>
<p begin="10916000000t" end="10938800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">全靠阿雷，我現在已經明白</p>
<p begin="10939600000t" end="10957200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">這個就是我想要的逃走計劃</p>
<p begin="10965200000t" end="10974800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">我已經決定了</p>
<p begin="10989600000t" end="11000000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">我是不會放棄的</p>
<p begin="11010400000t" end="11026000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">所以阿雷你讓步吧</p>
<p begin="11026800000t" end="11050000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">不要再在這裡跟我們爭吵，幫我們</p>
<p begin="11112400000t" end="11125200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">諾曼，你…</p>
<p begin="11126000000t" end="11146400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">我一定要帶全部人離開</p>
<p begin="11147200000t" end="11168400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">我不管，一定要這樣，不要…</p>
<p begin="11169200000t" end="11197600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">快管教一下這個傻丫頭，太硬來了</p>
<p begin="11198400000t" end="11231600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">是，真是的，看到她這樣精神就好</p>
<p begin="11232400000t" end="11252000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">不是說這個，快些阻止她</p>
<p begin="11252800000t" end="11267600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">你們都會沒命</p>
<p begin="11274400000t" end="11298800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">這一點你應該從一開始就知道</p>
<p begin="11316400000t" end="11338000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">當時艾瑪在哭</p>
<p begin="11349600000t" end="11364800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">那晚，我最初以為</p>
<p begin="11365600000t" end="11384000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">她是因為害怕所以才哭</p>
<p begin="11393600000t" end="11407200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">但是原來不是這樣</p>
<p begin="11417600000t" end="11431200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">當時我覺得很害怕</p>
<p begin="11432000000t" end="11443200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">以為自己會沒命</p>
<p begin="11450000000t" end="11481200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">但是艾瑪是因為怕家人會沒命</p>
<p begin="11482000000t" end="11492400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">所以才會哭</p>
<p begin="11501600000t" end="11513600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">她真的很厲害</p>
<p begin="11518800000t" end="11530800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">在當時那種情況下</p>
<p begin="11531600000t" end="11553200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">還可以考慮到要保護其他人</p>
<p begin="11554000000t" end="11569600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">但是做法不正確</p>
<p begin="11570400000t" end="11582400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">這樣是不會成功的</p>
<p begin="11583200000t" end="11594400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">如果只是我們三人</p>
<p begin="11601200000t" end="11612400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">或者有辦法逃脫</p>
<p begin="11632400000t" end="11645200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">你也沒做錯</p>
<p begin="11646000000t" end="11659600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">所以不用覺得不好意思</p>
<p begin="11665200000t" end="11689600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">不要因為感情而做錯判斷，諾曼</p>
<p begin="11698000000t" end="11708000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">不是這樣的，阿雷</p>
<p begin="11714800000t" end="11736400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">其實我也希望大家一起成功逃走</p>
<p begin="11750000000t" end="11762000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">為甚麼會這樣</p>
<p begin="11762800000t" end="11775200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">你應該不像她這樣</p>
<p begin="11786000000t" end="11796000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">你比她冷靜</p>
<p begin="11796800000t" end="11814000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">任何時候都能想出正確答案</p>
<p begin="11814800000t" end="11827200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">為甚麼你會變成這樣</p>
<p begin="11834400000t" end="11846000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">因為我喜歡她</p>
<p begin="11858400000t" end="11872400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">因為我喜歡艾瑪</p>
<p begin="11873200000t" end="11891200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">所以我希望她可以保持笑容</p>
<p begin="11909600000t" end="11920800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">實在太奇怪了</p>
<p begin="11928400000t" end="11946400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">就算艾瑪因為這樣而死也沒所謂嗎</p>
<p begin="11956400000t" end="11966000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">我會保護她</p>
<p begin="11978400000t" end="11994800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">為了可以達成這個目的</p>
<p begin="11995600000t" end="12011600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">就算要利用我也沒問題</p>
<p begin="12023600000t" end="12040800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">不過幸運的事就是</p>
<p begin="12041600000t" end="12060000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">我這麼多次決定了要做的事當中</p>
<p begin="12060800000t" end="12072000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">一次也沒有失敗過</p>
<p begin="12078400000t" end="12086000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">何況這個計劃</p>
<p begin="12086800000t" end="12103200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">未試過又怎麼知道一定不行</p>
<p begin="12108800000t" end="12117200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">我們逃走吧</p>
<p begin="12118000000t" end="12130800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">我們想出來的逃走計劃</p>
<p begin="12131600000t" end="12144000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">未必不會成功</p>
<p begin="12144800000t" end="12163600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">太瘋狂了　　可能是</p>
<p begin="12171200000t" end="12195200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">我跟艾瑪本來就已經很不正常</p>
<p begin="12196000000t" end="12212000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">可以說完全控制不了自己</p>
<p begin="12224800000t" end="12240400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">你應該不會不管我們吧</p>
<p begin="12269600000t" end="12300000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">可惡，我又怎麼會不理你們</p>
<p begin="12341200000t" end="12355600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">阿雷、諾曼</p>
<p begin="12356400000t" end="12376400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">現在應該還是自由時間吧</p>
<p begin="12382800000t" end="12393200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">發生甚麼事</p>
<p begin="12472800000t" end="12488800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">我給大家介紹</p>
<p begin="12489600000t" end="12514000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">這是我們這裡新來的妹妹，卡洛</p>
<p begin="12514800000t" end="12536400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">而這位就是克羅妮修女</p>
<p begin="12537200000t" end="12562000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">她是媽媽專程請回來的幫手</p>
<p begin="12572800000t" end="12592800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">是一個成年人？</p>
<p begin="12598400000t" end="12613200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">我們的敵人增加了</p>
<p begin="12633600000t" end="12659200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">從今天開始，我會跟大家一起生活</p>
<p begin="12660000000t" end="12674400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">請大家多多指教</p>
<p begin="12675200000t" end="12710800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">多多指教…</p>
<p begin="12912000000t" end="12936000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">(泛紅的天空)</p>
<p begin="12936800000t" end="12974000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">(如今看來如此恐怖)</p>
<p begin="12979200000t" end="12998800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">(若不知曉)</p>
<p begin="12999600000t" end="13034400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">(是否就能幸福度日)</p>
<p begin="13040400000t" end="13113200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">(又一盞溫暖的燈火悄悄熄滅)</p>
<p begin="13114000000t" end="13153200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">(不知不覺中失去了)</p>
<p begin="13154000000t" end="13213200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">(曾經誤信過　那溫柔的聲音)</p>
<p begin="13214000000t" end="13247600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">(那曾是我的一切)</p>
<p begin="13248400000t" end="13314000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">(憑著揮灑的汗水與熾熱的心)</p>
<p begin="13314800000t" end="13382000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">(我們的確抱著意志生存)</p>
<p begin="13382800000t" end="13420800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">(事到如今　還說甚麼想要你的愛)</p>
<p begin="13421600000t" end="13449200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">(動起來　不聽使喚的雙腿)</p>
<p begin="13450000000t" end="13482400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">(脫離這個牢籠)</p>
<p begin="13483200000t" end="13516000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">(抓緊明天的自由)</p>
<p begin="13516800000t" end="13548000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">(走出絕望的困境)</p>
</div>
